code: protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     GitHubEndpoint endpoint = new GitHubEndpoint(uri, this).     setProperties(endpoint, parameters).     String[] parts = remaining.split("/").     if (parts.length >= 1) {         String s = parts[0].         GitHubType type = getCamelContext().getTypeConverter().convertTo(GitHubType.class, s).         endpoint.setType(type).         if (parts.length > 1) {             s = parts[1].             endpoint.setBranchName(s).         }     }     return endpoint. }
